            requested task fascinates me. Because of this interest, I began studying 
            programming languages, and I began to learn languages with my dad. From 
            my senior year of high school to now, my fifth year of college, I have 
            gained an intermediate background in Python, R, HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.
            While pursuing these studies, I learned a basic level of web development,
            and I published my first professional website for my fraternity, The
            <a href="https://www.preshousegtown.org">President's House Association</a>
