            freshman campaign, I transferred to Georgetown College in Georgetown, KY to 
            continue my academic and athletic endeavors. Throughout my time as an athlete,
            I have learned the immense importance of dedication to the sport. There is a 
            striking difference in athletic performance when you stick to the little things
            like diet and sleep/recovery, and there is a lot that must be done in training,
