            dedicating myself to all aspects of training intelligently and effectively, and
            I carry this determination into my career and educational desires as well.
            In May 2019, I will graduate with a Bachelor of Science in Data Analysis, and
            I am excited to get out into the world and put my passions to work in the 
            professional world. There are big things coming.
